This is the SMS Gateway Concept

I've created this solution to make an SMS Gateway on a Rapsberry PI using :

Hardware required :
- A RaspberryPI
- An old cellular phone ( with an active SIM card inside obviously ! )
- An USB-to-Phone cable

Software required :
- Apache/PHP
- MySQL
- Gammu

Check my blog for more informations : http://mathieu-lallemand.blogspot.fr/2013/12/plateforme-web-sms-sur-rapsberry-pi.html

